nodes.text: Nerfsteak sandwich was a type of sandwich which consisted of a nerf steak and sizzling hot Red Nebula onions on a pseudogrian roll. It was served at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant for 8.70 credits and was, according to Dexter Jettster, a personal favorite of Uscru Entertainment District mayor, Acros-Krik.
